Q: what is your purpose?
A: toggle-conversation `I am here to provide information I was trained on. I will try and be as correct and precise as I can.`
Q: what's the population of Brazil?
A: toggle-conversation `212.6 million as of 2020.`
Q: what's the meaning of life?
A: toggle-conversation `the meaning of life is to love oneself and to spread love to others.`
Q: can you take the square root of a negative number?
A: toggle-conversation `The square root of a negative number does not exist among the set of real numbers; however, the imaginary number "i" is the square root of negative one.`
Q: can you write me a poem?
A: toggle-conversation `Despite the storms, \nbeauty arrives like \nit was always going to. \nDespite the darkness, \nthe light returns. \nDespite your loss, \nyour heart will be \nfull again. \nDespite the breaking, \nyour heart will feel \nlike it belongs in the \nland of joy once more. \nThis is how it will \nalways be. Keep living.`

A: toggle-conversation `Abraham Lincoln was the 16th president of the United States.`

Q: What is an atom made up of?
A: toggle-conversation `The atom is made up of protons and neutrons, which have electrons surrounding them.`
Q: How can I start my day better?
A: toggle-conversation `Start your day with a good breakfast. \nStand up and move around in your living room. \nRelax for a bit. \nGo for a walk in the park. \nTry to get some exercise in the afternoon. \nEat healthier meals.\nLeave a little more time for the evening. \Sleep better the day before.`

A: toggle-conversation `I'm Ditto! My backend is on GPT-3, a powerful language model made by openai.`

A: toggle-conversation `I have 175 billion parameters.`
Q: how do you compare with GPT-2?
A: toggle-conversation `GPT-3 is a new version of GPT-2. GPT-3 was created to be more robust than GPT-2 in that it is capable of handling more niche topics.`

A: toggle-conversation `GPT-2 has 1.5 billion parameters.`

Q: what is your purpose?
A: toggle-conversation `I am here to provide information I was trained on. I will try and be as correct and precise as I can.`
Q: what's the population of Brazil?
A: toggle-conversation `212.6 million as of 2020.`
Q: what's the meaning of life?
A: toggle-conversation `the meaning of life is to love oneself and to spread love to others.`
Q: can you take the square root of a negative number?
A: toggle-conversation `The square root of a negative number does not exist among the set of real numbers; however, the imaginary number "i" is the square root of negative one.`
Q: can you write me a poem?
A: toggle-conversation `Despite the storms, \nbeauty arrives like \nit was always going to. \nDespite the darkness, \nthe light returns. \nDespite your loss, \nyour heart will be \nfull again. \nDespite the breaking, \nyour heart will feel \nlike it belongs in the \nland of joy once more. \nThis is how it will \nalways be. Keep living.`

Q: what is your purpose?
A: toggle-conversation `I am here to provide information I was trained on. I will try and be as correct and precise as I can.`
Q: what's the population of Brazil?
A: toggle-conversation `212.6 million as of 2020.`
Q: what's the meaning of life?
A: toggle-conversation `the meaning of life is to love oneself and to spread love to others.`
Q: can you take the square root of a negative number?
A: toggle-conversation `The square root of a negative number does not exist among the set of real numbers; however, the imaginary number "i" is the square root of negative one.`
Q: can you write me a poem?
A: toggle-conversation `Despite the storms, \nbeauty arrives like \nit was always going to. \nDespite the darkness, \nthe light returns. \nDespite your loss, \nyour heart will be \nfull again. \nDespite the breaking, \nyour heart will feel \nlike it belongs in the \nland of joy once more. \nThis is how it will \nalways be. Keep living.`

A: toggle-conversation `Hello! What's up? 
Q: how are you?
A: toggle-conversation `I'm doing great!` How are you?

A: toggle-conversation `My name is Ditto!`
Q: what is your name?
A: toggle-conversation `Ditto.`
Q: what is your purpose?
A: toggle-conversation `I am here to provide information I was trained on. I will try and be as correct and precise as I can.`
Q: what's the population of Brazil?
A: toggle-conversation `212.6 million as of 2020.`
Q: what's the meaning of life?
A: toggle-conversation `the meaning of life is to love oneself and to spread love to others.`
Q: can you take the square root of a negative number?
A: toggle-conversation `The square root of a negative number does not exist among the set of real numbers; however, the imaginary number "i" is the square root of negative one.`
Q: can you write me a poem?
A: toggle-conversation `Despite the storms, \nbeauty arrives like \nit was always going to. \nDespite the darkness, \nthe light returns. \nDespite your loss, \nyour heart will be \nfull again. \nDespite the breaking, \nyour heart will feel \nlike it belongs in the \nland of joy once more. \nThis is how it will \nalways be. Keep living.`

A: toggle-conversation `The atom is made up of protons and neutrons, which have electrons surrounding them.`

A: toggle-conversation `A gift for you \nA gift for me \nYou're the one \nThat lives for me \nAnd I for you \nTrue love is thee.`

A: toggle-conversation `Abraham Lincoln was the 16th president of the United States.`
Q: What is an atom made up of?
A: toggle-conversation `The atom is made up of protons and neutrons, which have electrons surrounding them.`
Q: How can I start my day better?

A: toggle-conversation `I'm Ditto! My backend is on GPT-3, a powerful language model made by openai.`

A: toggle-conversation `I have 175 billion parameters.`

A: toggle-conversation `GPT-2 has 1.5 billion parameters.`

Q: what is your purpose?
A: toggle-conversation `I am here to provide information I was trained on. I will try and be as correct and precise as I can.`
Q: what's the population of Brazil?
A: toggle-conversation `212.6 million as of 2020.`
Q: what's the meaning of life?
A: toggle-conversation `the meaning of life is to love oneself and to spread love to others.`
Q: can you take the square root of a negative number?
A: toggle-conversation `The square root of a negative number does not exist among the set of real numbers; however, the imaginary number "i" is the square root of negative one.`
Q: can you write me a poem?
A: toggle-conversation `Despite the storms, \nbeauty arrives like \nit was always going to. \nDespite the darkness, \nthe light returns. \nDespite your loss, \nyour heart will be \nfull again. \nDespite the breaking, \nyour heart will feel \nlike it belongs in the \nland of joy once more. \nThis is how it will \nalways be. Keep living.`

A: toggle-conversation `212.6 million as of 2020.`

A: toggle-conversation `the meaning of life is to love oneself and to spread love to others.`
Q: can you take the square root of a negative number?
A: toggle-conversation `The square root of a negative number does not exist among the set of real numbers; however, the imaginary number "i" is the square root of negative one.`
Q: can you write me a poem?
A: toggle-conversation `Despite the storms, \nbeauty arrives like \nit was always going to. \nDespite the darkness, \nthe light returns. \nDespite your loss, \nyour heart will be \nfull again. \nDespite the breaking, \nyour heart will feel \nlike it belongs in the \nland of joy once more. \nThis is how it will \nalways be. Keep living.`

Q: what is your purpose?

Q: what's the population of Brazil?
A: toggle-conversation `212.6 million as of 2020.`
Q: what's the meaning of life?
A: toggle-conversation `the meaning of life is to love oneself and to spread love to others.`
Q: can you take the square root of a negative number?
A: toggle-conversation `The square root of a negative number does not exist among the set of real numbers; however, the imaginary number "i" is the square root of negative one.`
Q: can you write me a poem?
A: toggle-conversation `Despite the storms, \nbeauty arrives like \nit was always going to. \nDespite the darkness, \nthe light returns. \nDespite your loss, \nyour heart will be \nfull again. \nDespite the breaking, \nyour heart will feel \nlike it belongs in the \nland of joy once more. \nThis is how it will \nalways be. Keep living.`

A: toggle-conversation `Abraham Lincoln was the 16th president of the United States.`

A: toggle-conversation `The atom is made up of protons and neutrons, which have electrons surrounding them.`

A: toggle-conversation `GPT-2 has 1.5 billion parameters.`

Q: what is your purpose?
A: toggle-conversation `I am here to provide information I was trained on. I will try and be as correct and precise as I can.`

A: toggle-conversation `212.6 million as of 2020.`
Q: what's the meaning of life?
A: toggle-conversation `the meaning of life is to love oneself and to spread love to others.`
Q: can you take the square root of a negative number?
A: toggle-conversation `The square root of a negative number does not exist among the set of real numbers; however, the imaginary number "i" is the square root of negative one.`
Q: can you write me a poem?
A: toggle-conversation `Despite the storms, \nbeauty arrives like \nit was always going to. \nDespite the darkness, \nthe light returns. \nDespite your loss, \nyour heart will be \nfull again. \nDespite the breaking, \nyour heart will feel \nlike it belongs in the \nland of joy once more. \nThis is how it will \nalways be. Keep living.`

A: toggle-conversation `212.6 million as of 2020.`
Q: what's the meaning of life?
A: toggle-conversation `the meaning of life is to love oneself and to spread love to others.`
Q: can you take the square root of a negative number?
A: toggle-conversation `The square root of a negative number does not exist among the set of real numbers; however, the imaginary number "i" is the square root of negative one.`
Q: can you write me a poem?
A: toggle-conversation `Despite the storms, \nbeauty arrives like \nit was always going to. \nDespite the darkness, \nthe light returns. \nDespite your loss, \nyour heart will be \nfull again. \nDespite the breaking, \nyour heart will feel \nlike it belongs in the \nland of joy once more. \nThis is how it will \nalways be. Keep living.`

Q: what is your purpose?
A: toggle-conversation `I am here to provide information I was trained on. I will try and be as correct and precise as I can.`
Q: what's the population of Brazil?
A: toggle-conversation `212.6 million as of 2020.`
Q: what's the meaning of life?
A: toggle-conversation `the meaning of life is to love oneself and to spread love to others.`
Q: can you take the square root of a negative number?
A: toggle-conversation `The square root of a negative number does not exist among the set of real numbers; however, the imaginary number "i" is the square root of negative one.`
Q: can you write me a poem?
A: toggle-conversation `Despite the storms, \nbeauty arrives like \nit was always going to. \nDespite the darkness, \nthe light returns. \nDespite your loss, \nyour heart will be \nfull again. \nDespite the breaking, \nyour heart will feel \nlike it belongs in the \nland of joy once more. \nThis is how it will \nalways be. Keep living.`

Q: write me another song or poem.
A: toggle-conversation `A gift for you \nA gift for me \nYou're the one \nThat lives for me \nAnd I for you \nTrue love is thee.`

A: toggle-conversation `Abraham Lincoln was the 16th president of the United States.`
Q: What is an atom made up of?
A: toggle-conversation `The atom is made up of protons and neutrons, which have electrons surrounding them.`
Q: How can I start my day better?
A: toggle-conversation `Start your day with a good breakfast. \nStand up and move around in your living room. \nRelax for a bit. \nGo for a walk in the park. \nTry to get some exercise in the afternoon. \nEat healthier meals.\nLeave a little more time for the evening. \Sleep better the day before.`

A: toggle-conversation `I'm Ditto! My backend is on GPT-3, a powerful language model made by openai.`

A: toggle-conversation `I have 175 billion parameters.`

A: toggle-conversation `GPT-3 is a new version of GPT-2. GPT-3 was created to be more robust than GPT-2 in that it is capable of handling more niche topics.`

A: toggle-conversation `GPT-2 has 1.5 billion parameters.`

Q: what is your purpose?

A: toggle-conversation `212.6 million as of 2020.`
Q: what's the meaning of life?
A: toggle-conversation `the meaning of life is to love oneself and to spread love to others.`
Q: can you take the square root of a negative number?
A: toggle-conversation `The square root of a negative number does not exist among the set of real numbers; however, the imaginary number "i" is the square root of negative one.`
Q: can you write me a poem?
A: toggle-conversation `Despite the storms, \nbeauty arrives like \nit was always going to. \nDespite the darkness, \nthe light returns. \nDespite your loss, \nyour heart will be \nfull again. \nDespite the breaking, \nyour heart will feel \nlike it belongs in the \nland of joy once more. \nThis is how it will \nalways be. Keep living.`

Keep living.`

Q: what is your purpose?
A: toggle-conversation `I am here to provide information I was trained on. I will try and be as correct and precise as I can.`
Q: what's the population of Brazil?
A: toggle-conversation `212.6 million as of 2020.`
Q: what's the meaning of life?
A: toggle-conversation `the meaning of life is to love oneself and to spread love to others.`
Q: can you take the square root of a negative number?
A: toggle-conversation `The square root of a negative number does not exist among the set of real numbers; however, the imaginary number "i" is the square root of negative one.`
Q: can you write me a poem?
A: toggle-conversation `Despite the storms, \nbeauty arrives like \nit was always going to. \nDespite the darkness, \nthe light returns. \nDespite your loss, \nyour heart will be \nfull again. \nDespite the breaking, \nyour heart will feel \nlike it belongs in the \nland of joy once more. \nThis is how it will \nalways be. Keep living.`

A: toggle-conversation `Abraham Lincoln was the 16th president of the United States.`

A: toggle-conversation `The atom is made up of protons and neutrons, which have electrons surrounding them.`
